duties_responsibilities.duty: Develop and implement dietary plans tailored to individual patients.
Provide nutrition assessments, counseling, and education to patients.
Coordinate with interdisciplinary teams and maintain accurate medical records.
Teach patients how to read and interpret nutrition labels and establish realistic goals.

education_certification.credential: Registered Dietitian/Nutritionist with the Commission on Dietetic Registration (CDR)
Bachelor's degree in Nutrition, Dietetics, or related fields
